productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Allean has one of these. She works as a sky diver and she says it looks weedy.
I saw one of these in Cote d'Ivoire and I bought one.
SoCal cockroaches are unwelcome, crafty, and tenacious. This mesh keeps them away.
one of my hobbies is drawing. and when i'm drawing this works great.
